From dd01a7313efbd82f9ed68aaf02a034fb78b9e5ce Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: tamirhussain-ai <tamirhussain@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 11 Mar 2026 22:19:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Phase 1b: Add email allowlist access control

- authContext: allowlist check on every login, bootstrap first user as admin
- AccessDenied.tsx: friendly screen for unauthorized university users
- AllowlistManager.tsx: admin UI to add/remove/bulk-import allowed emails with roles
- AdminSettings: new Access Control tab (admin only)
- Login: shows AccessDenied page if email not on allowlist
